<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
aspit wrote:<BR>
<DIV>Hi FIX CLASSES NOBODY CARES ABOUT A RETARDED SYSTEM.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Dropping nonpvp zones is a good thing, tranq should have never ever been a non pvp zone.&nbsp; All it does is encourage zerging and bind rushing.&nbsp; Secondly scrap the point system, its a piece of crap.&nbsp; Nobody gives a damn about a system, what they do care about is balancing classes in pvp.&nbsp; Lets pull our heads out of your @#$ for once in our lives and fix the problem instead of trying to bandaid it sony.&nbsp; You can read everyones problems with overpowered items and abilities so the solution is very very clear.&nbsp; Cut tranq and nexus from non pvp.&nbsp; I wish pok would get cut also, but its really not a huge issue since im not opposed to having a non pvp tradeskill zone, since baz tradeskill vendors are extremely limited.&nbsp; People dont play on pvp servers for rewards, they play because its fun to kill someone who you dont like.&nbsp; The rewards for pvp are self fullfilling, there is no need for a gimmick system.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Mistake number 2:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Listening to every bluebie whiner who has nothing at stake here and is 100% clueless as to the state of a pvp server.&nbsp; This includes listening to clueless idiots posting on here about what thy "think" pvp servers are like and how the changes may effect their "ideas".&nbsp; This also includes setting up a beta pvp server where im sure the majority of the testers have never played on a pvp server.&nbsp; Obviously the first time they get owned they are going to /feedback this system sucks scrap it.&nbsp; I cant believe that you would be so incompetent as to test apples and oranges.&nbsp; If you want to test pvp issues test them on live pvp servers, not in a room full of clueless bluebies.</DIV><BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
<DIV></DIV>**Fluffernutter** i have to say i agree completely with Aspit. someone shoot me please. My main concern is definately PoT as a safe zone and Class balance. Fix these 2 and ill be more then happy
