<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
cyberfire wrote:<BR>
<P>phroak, they can't keep you perma mezzed if you use your head... you could buy crimsinpotions, or stinging wart potions... also (because we all know that Aerist don't pvp without 20+ people and 10-15 defiant / zeph) just /gu i am mezzed, hit me... and omg, your unmezzed... </P>
