			>
			<STRONG><U></U></STRONG>
<DIV>This is gonna be LONG. This post should be reviewed by EVERYONE. Please feel free to pick apart ANYTHING that you think I have wrong here. This is an attempt to specifically describe changes that would "Balance" EQ PvP. Sony obviously doesn't have a clue, since they all play on blue servers anyway. I can prove that they don't play on PvP servers! Ever try to get a GM? Its nearly impossible on PvP servers.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>PLEASE NOTE: This is specifically for TEAM servers, NOT Rallos or Sullon. Some of these ideas could be used for them, but they are Very different in almost every PvP aspect from Vallon and Tallon. (Vallon and Tallon show how creative Sony can be, they changed 1 letter in the names of both servers.)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>NOTE TO SONY: I WILL verbally /bash you in this post, since you have failed at so many attempts in EQ, and this looks like another, I don't feel I owe you the privaledge of respect at this point. After all, I pay to beta test a game that still hasn't had its original parts fixed. 5 years is a long time for a game to exist /congrats on that, but seriously. Have you ever released an expansion that worked? Kunark wasn't that bad, but I still have nightmares of Luclin. That was patcher hell when it went live. It didn't even have the bazaar /trader or /bazaar included, even though they were part of that expansion. DO NOT GET AHEAD OF YOURSELVES HERE. It would/could/WILL ruin game play. sorry if I get a bit out of line, but I've been playing a long time, I know how the system works. /ooc Darn PoK bug got me again. /ooc I'm back, sorry, EQ locked on me. I had to reset the comp... Again.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Ok, now that I have my insults out of the way, here is what I see as current issues, and possible fixes.</DIV>
<DIV>Race/Class Combinations. (Currently on all servers)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Barbarian - BST, BER, ROG, SHM, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>Dark Elf - CLR, ENC, MAG, NEC, ROG, SK, WAR, WIZ</DIV>
<DIV>Dwarf - BER, CLR, PAL, ROG, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>Erudite - CLR, ENC, MAG, NEC, PAL, SK, WIZ</DIV>
<DIV>Froglok - CLR, PAL, SHM, WAR, WIZ</DIV>
<DIV>Gnome - CLR, ENC, MAG, NEC, PAL, ROG, SK, WAR, WIZ</DIV>
<DIV>Half Elf - BRD, DRU, PAL, RNG, ROG, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>Halfling - CLR, DRU, PAL, RNG, ROG, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>High Elf - CLR, ENC, MAG, PAL, WIZ</DIV>
<DIV>Human - BRD, CLR, DRU, ENC, MAG, MNK, NEC, PAL, RNG, ROG, SK, WAR, WIZ</DIV>
<DIV>Iksar - BST, MNK, NEC, SK, SHM, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>Ogre - BST, BER, SK, SHM, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>Troll - BST, BER, SK, SHM, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>Vah Shir - BRD, BST, BER, ROG, SHM, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>Wood Elf - BRD, DRU, RNG, ROG, WAR</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Teams (On Vallon and Tallon Zek)</DIV>
<DIV>Blue (human) Team - BAR, ERU, FRG, HUM, VAH</DIV>
<DIV>Orange (evil) Team - DE, OGR, TRL, IKS</DIV>
<DIV>Purple (shorty (peck)) Team - DWF, GNM, Halfling</DIV>
<DIV>Yellow (elf (fef)) Team - Half Elf, High elf, Wood elf</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Okay, now to fix current issues with just these aspects.</DIV>
